Emma Puttick, the creative mind behind Naudic, is opening up her world to travellers in need of a little inspiration. For over a decade, Emma has drawn creative energy from almost every corner of the globe, channelling it into each collection she creates. Naudic Round The Globe presents a different type of travel experience.  One that will ignite the creative mind, no matter what your passion or craft may be.
